        <section id="fitness" class="content-section">
            <h2>Fitness Coaching Tips</h2>
            <p>Explore these fitness coaching strategies for a well-rounded approach to health:</p>
            <div class="grid-container">
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>1. Strength Training</h3>
                    <p>Focus on compound exercises like squats, deadlifts, and bench presses to build strength and muscle.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>2. Interval Training</h3>
                    <p>Incorporate high-intensity interval training (HIIT) to maximize calorie burn in less time.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>3. Nutrition Balance</h3>
                    <p>Eat a diet rich in proteins, healthy fats, and complex carbohydrates for sustained energy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>4. Flexibility Training</h3>
                    <p>Include yoga or Pilates to improve flexibility, posture, and core strength.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>5. Hydration</h3>
                    <p>Drink at least 8 glasses of water daily to stay hydrated and enhance performance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>6. Goal Setting</h3>
                    <p>Set realistic fitness goals and break them into smaller milestones to stay motivated.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>7. Rest & Recovery</h3>
                    <p>Prioritize rest days to allow your muscles to recover and prevent overtraining.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>8. Progress Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Keep a workout journal to track your progress and identify areas for improvement.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>9. Personalized Plans</h3>
                    <p>Work with a certified coach to tailor a fitness plan that aligns with your goals and lifestyle.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <h3>10. Mental Resilience</h3>
                    <p>Develop a positive mindset and stay consistent to overcome challenges in your fitness journey.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
